               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Wright's Defence.</hi> I went over the water, and coming back, I met this young man by the railway station; he was coming my way; I stopped to look over the bridge once or twice; he came to me, and said, "Come on;" we went across, and he pulled me to an arch, and the constable took me; the purse was found in my pocket, but I do not know anything of it; I am inno<lb></lb>cent of it.</p>
